    ENDIF.

*For From Zone
    READ TABLE LT_IFLO INTO LS_IFLO WITH KEY TPLNR = LS_VIQMEL-TPLNR BINARY SEARCH.
    IF SY-SUBRC = 0.
      "  MOVE LS_IFLO-EQFNR TO GS_MAIN-FROM_ZONE.
      CLEAR GS_MAIN-CURR_LOC .
      FREE TEXT_TAB.
      FREE LV_ZONE.
      IF LS_VIQMEL-TPLNR  IS NOT INITIAL.
